{
  "stem": "521.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was just surprised that the Germans had the ambition to build a brand new camp for Jews, but they did it anyway.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now there we had this idiotic SS people who were just shooting into barracks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if somebody was shot, he was yelling, I got shot, and then dropped dead.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then he ordered somebody to pick him up and take him out and bury.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Once I was so lucky that somebody who has died in our barrack, and he told me, now you pick him up and bury him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we had those wheelbarrows, and I had to put the man into a wheelbarrow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was supposed to take him some distance from the camp, not a long distance, and I was digging a hole, a very shallow hole.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I put the man in, and I covered it with some dirt.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I mean, I couldn't dig a six feet grave anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was just too tired.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was the time when I started to feel very, very tired.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "As I was walking, I was walking in a kind of a daze.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I knew where I'm going to walk, but I didn't know that I am going to make it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before or during?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were liberated, I was liberated on May the 4th.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it must have been 10 days or so.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About the liberation, now all of a sudden we saw that all the guards of the camp-- except the SS, SS were running away about a day or two before the end of the war, and they were throwing grenade into his gun, or whatever he had.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so blow it up and he was changing clothing and disappeared.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
